Description:
INSPECTION BY PRIVATE APPOINTMENT ANYTIME.
The discerning buyer will immediately recognise the value and appeal of this great family home. Tucked into a quiet court location and literally a stones throw to the magnificent Members Clubhouse, 5 Kelly Terrace is the type of home to suit so many different families.
Built by Henley Homes and offering an interactive floor plan, this is the home for either young families or teenagers alike.
As you enter the home you will find a generous study to the front with double bi fold doors. This is the perfect space for those working from home or VCE students.
The large lounge at the centre of the property could also double as a billiard room if desired.
Opposite this room is a great spot which could be used as a home theatre or 5th bedroom for guests or elderly parents.
This is serviced by a full bathroom downstairs.
The gourmet kitchen with granite bench tops and stainless steel appliances presides over the family and dining area. Double sliding doors lead outside to the pretty rear garden with established trees and plants.
Upstairs are 4 large bedrooms. The master suite has a lovely ensuite with spa bath and double basins whilst the other 3 rooms all offer built in robes.
A comfortable sitting room upstairs provides another living zone for family members.
Low maintenance gardens and paths surround the home so you can take advantage of the lifestyle benefits Sandhurst offers so many of.

Description:
Move right in
Move right in
Stylishly appointed with warm timber floors and fully updated, this home is ready for you to move right in with space to entertain.
The new kitchen has a gas cooktop, oven, dishwasher, large pantry, stone benchtops, breakfast bar, and overlooks the open plan dining and living areas. The large glass sliding doors allow for an effortless transition to the decked outdoor entertaining area. A reverse cycle split system will keep you comfortable year-round, and in winter, you will be warm and toasty in front of the wood heater. A vast hall takes you to the three double bedrooms. the master benefits from a walk-in robe while the remaining bedrooms have built-in robes and are serviced by a luxuriously updated central bathroom
On 640sqm approx., A generous undercover alfresco area overlooks the lush lawn and beyond into the sunny garden. this perfect starter or retiree's nest is equipped with plenty of extra features including solar hot water,16 solar panels. vegetable garden, Shed and extensive parking
In this blissful location in a gorgeous coastal village, this happy home is a short walk to the beach, pier, nature reserves, playgrounds, and the bus, as well as the general store to get what you need or your Friday night fish 'n' chips, while within 15 minutes of Cranbourne shopping hub, Pearcedale Primary School, the Tooradin shopping and cafe precinct, and great family amenities.

Description:
BRAND NEW QUALITY ORBIT HOME IN HIGHGROVE
Please call Agent to arrange an inspection - Only 1 Person at a time!!!
INSPECTIONS BY APPOINTMENT ONLY.
(Offers closing by 13th July @ 5PM unless sold prior)
Found in the sold-out Highgrove estate sits this lovely, BRAND NEW four-bedroom home by Orbit homes. Ideal for growing families and investors alike there is plenty to love about this home from its convenient location to the long list of quality inclusions. Everything is done and ready for the new lucky owner to move in or lease straight away!
Features include:
Large master suite with walk in robes and its own en-suite.
Three further spacious bedrooms all with built in robes
Generous open plan living and dining area
Well-equipped central kitchen with all the bells and whistles freestanding 900mm oven with built in rangehood, dishwasher, 20mm stone benches, pot draws, breakfast bar and plenty of cupboard and bench space.
Family bathroom as well as separate toilet
Undercover alfresco overlooking the low maintenance backyard
Double garage with internal access to the home
Extras include: Ducted heating, solar hot water system, low maintenance landscaped gardens, quality floor coverings and fixtures, ceiling fans to all bedrooms, downlights throughout, new fencing plus loads more!
Highgrove estate was designed with family and community living in mind, with multiple parklands and avenues linking neighborhoods. Just a short walk away you can find a children's park and playground plus the home is ideally located close to a multitude of other facilities including childcare, schools, Casey Recreation and Aquatic Centre, multiple schools, Shopping on Clyde, public transport and all Clyde North has to offer.

***PHOTO ID REQUIRED AT ALL INSPECTIONS***

Description:
Exceptional Value
Nestled in a fantastic pocket in central Cranbourne sits this lovely 4-bedroom home offering generous living space as well as a convenient lifestyle. Enjoying a quiet location within a family-friendly neighbourhood, this quality brick veneer home unites privacy and space, making it tremendously appealing to first home buyers and young families craving that extra bit of space occupying approx. 652m2 of land.
Newly renovated comprising L shape lounge/dining, separate family/meals, four spacious bedrooms and large rear garden. All situated in a quiet court with side access to fit your boat or trailer this home will be snapped up in no time.
Generous outdoor entertaining area, leaves plenty of room for entertaining your guests all year around and still leaving space for the kids to play. Parking won't be an issue at this property, as this home caters for multiple vehicles, with its extensive driveway
This home is position PERFECT within walking distance to all major amenities in a highly desirable area. Less than 500m away you'll find Cranbourne West Primary School & Duff St shopping precinct, adjacent to the J & P Cam reserve where the local footy team resides and not to mention only a 3 min drive will see you are at Cranbourne Train Station. This is a golden opportunity not to be missed!

Description:
Reaching for the Stars!
Prominently situated on an elevated corner in the popular Livingston Estate is this sleek double story Porter Davis build has everything that you could want and is ready to be called yours! Built with four bedrooms plus study nook and three bathrooms, this property sitting at 2 Hammersmith Way appeals to those who are wanting the ultimate lifestyle pad.
With speakers built in, wired and ready for you to plug in and play to the internal living and decked alfresco area, double glazed windows, granite tops feature in the majority of wet areas and blockout blinds throughout, as well as an additional alarm system that is integrated into the garage, the property seeks the highest level of comfort whilst maintaining elegance and integrity of being a free flowing design layout. You will not need to worry about storage in this property as there is built in cabinetry in the open living area, additional storage in the laundry, built in robes in all bedrooms with sliding doors and a unique storage area underneath the stairs. Omega and Blanco appliances occupy the kitchen alongside soft close drawers and a walk-in pantry. Master suite features a double vanity en-suite and walk-in dressing robe with all other bedrooms being sized to fit a queen bed. Evaporative cooling and ducted heating serving further comfortability. Leading to the idyllic outdoor area is an undercover alfresco area as well as a designed retaining wall embrace landscaped gardens with inbuilt bench seats so you can entertain at all times of the year! Added potential to integrate further side access.
Within walking distance to the infamous Casey Fields, supermarket, parks, childcare centres and public transport you will not be short of amenities! The Livingston Estate lives up to its name and is a community you will want to be apart of.
Come and visit this property today! Ensure to leave your mobile number upon enquires as ones without will not be returned to.

Description:
Cre8. Negoti8. Celebr8!
Stunning Family Home In A Great Location!
Affordable First Home Or Investment Opportunity
Nestled in the Clarinda Park Estate of Cranbourne West is this beautiful X-Display family home ready for you to move in.
Located on 448m2 in the sought-after Clarinda Park Estate, this house ticks all the boxes. Designed with high-end family living in mind, no cost has been spared in this X-Display home. Premium inclusions all add to the WOW factor!
There are 3 generous sized bedrooms, the master bedroom has a large walk in ensuite, walk in robe. The remaining 2 bedrooms have built in double wardrobes and are serviced by the main bathroom which includes a bath tub.
The open plan kitchen features stainless steel appliances including a five burner cook top, a large oven and dishwasher, a massive walk in pantry and an island benchtop which looks out onto the family meals area where the whole family can congregate.

Description:
Space, comfort & contemporary family style
Ultra-stylish and ready for effortless family living, this impeccable 4-bedroom residence delivers the laid back lifestyle appeal while surrounded by a pretty landscaped walking trail, as far as position is concerned, this is unbeatable! This great home will suit a broad range of buyers, from empty nesters looking for a lifestyle change, to young families seeking the friendly community Sandhurst is renowned for.
With a beautifully designed layout for the modern family, you'll enjoy two light filled living areas including a large versatile rumpus room plus a huge casual open-plan living zone overlooked by a stunning kitchen with island bench, 600mm oven, gas cooktop, large pantry and stainless-steel appliances. Year-round entertaining is a breeze with sliding doors extending the indoors onto a lovely undercover alfresco zone, grassed yard, low maintenance landscaped gardens and handy gate to the walking trail behind the home. Accommodation boasts a sophisticated en-suited main retreat complete with walk-in robe, three further bedrooms all (BIRs), a glossy modern family bathroom and separate w/c.
Appointed with ducted heating, evaporative cooling, full-sized laundry with storage, double car garage with external and internal entry plus low-maintenance gardens. Not to mention, unlimited recycled water and family membership to all the amenities Sandhurst has become renowned for!
Positioned within a leisurely walk to parkland, reserves and golf plus close proximity to shopping, schools and transport links.
Call now to book your private appointment today as this wonderful property won't last long!

PRICED TO SELL !! - Immaculate 4 bed, 2 bath, 2 car
A fine example of modern luxury and contemporary finesse. this sublime single-level home delivers stylish finishes with low-maintenance ease amidst beautiful landscaped gardens. Deluxe finishes and brilliant natural light are recurring themes throughout generous open-plan living/dining, where a spectacular galley-style kitchen boasting stainless steel appliances and ample storage tells a story of efficiency. Lifestyle flexibility is confirmed by 4 robed bedrooms (main bedroom with ensuite/WIR) and central bathroom, whilst ducted heating, split system AC and large double garage with internal access enhance lifestyle appeal. The home is currently leased to a fantastic tenant for $1,695 PCM making it the ideal investment. Located in a quiet court setting, close to schools, public transport including Merinda Park and Cranbourne Train Stations, Marriot Waters shopping centre and parklands.

Description:
SWEET & CHARMING FAMILY HOME (PLEASE CONTACT AGENT TO ORGANISE AN INSPECTION)
CRANBOURNE WEST - Sitting in a quiet spot in Cranbourne West sits 24 Marnie Drive and this home represents the perfect opportunity to get into the property market.
From the entry of the home, you are greeted with a beautiful, sunny and well sized living area with new floating floorboards, creating an immediate impression of warmth. The living space is complete with both a gas wall furnace, and split system ensuring climate control is never an issue.
Continuing on, the kitchen and meals area is sized for a family and presents as nice and cheery. Featuring new quality tiles, four gas burner stove top, plenty of bench and cupboard space, this open plan kitchen and meals area is the perfect set up and a great space to spend time prepping family meals.
At 24 Marnie, you will find 3 good sized bedrooms. The master is equipped with enough space for a study nook, a ceiling fan and access to the main bathroom. A gorgeous feature wall brings homeliness to this room. The additional 2 bedrooms are sunny, with plenty of light.
The bedrooms are serviced by the recently renovated main bathroom, which is functional and tidy.
Stepping outside you will be greeted with a paved entertainment area with large pergola, perfect for extending out the meals area when the weather is pleasant.
The property also features a carport with side access into the backyard, along with a shed for extra storage.
Features include:
- Gas wall furnace
- New floating floorboards
- New quality tiles
- Recently renovated bathroom
- Open plan kitchen and meals area
- Paved entertainment area
Cranbourne West is a fast developing and family friendly area. Offering a great combination of schools including Cranbourne West Primary, and St Peter's College. The area provides easy access to main arterial roads including the Monash Freeway and East Link and is very popular with families and investors. Access to public transport including Merinda Park Station and Cranbourne Train Station is close by.
At Ray White Cranbourne our price indications are based upon probable market value, the likely selling price and vendor expectations. You can view with confidence that vendors will sell within the range with favourable conditions

Description:
Golf Course View!
This spacious home backs onto one of two Golf Courses in Sandhurst. This view has to be seen, to be believed! The home comprising 3 large bedrooms features walk in robe and ensuite in master and built in robes in the 2 other bedrooms.
The kitchen/ meals and family area is modern and tiled throughout. The lovely modern kitchen with all the mod cons. The rear lounge features a sliding door to the covered alfesco area and great sized backyard with that stunning view of the Golf Course! OTHER FEATURES INCLUDE: * Ducted heating *
* Alarm system * Dishwasher * Double garage with remote control and internal access TAKE ADVANTAGE OF ALL THAT SANDHURST HAS TO OFFER: * Use of the Sandhurst Health and Fitness Club with indoor pool, gym, tennis courts included in the rent (for two people) * 50% of the Estate is dedicated to green open space & parklands * 50 Kilometres of walking, cycling & cart paths * Fibre optic network for phone & internet through Clublinks * Recycled water for garden and car washing; and * 24 hour on site security * Clubhouse with restaurant & bar * Sandhurst is located within easy reach of EastLink, Peninsula Link, Port Phillip Bay at Carrum and the Mornington Peninsula, offering convenience while maintaining a country club feel. **Please note, this is a non Smoking property (internally) Pets allowed by application VIEW BY OPEN FOR INSPECTION OR BY APPOINTMENT 8787 9000

WHERE SIZE AND QUALITY COUNTS (FULL WALK THROUGH VIDEO OF HOME AVAILABLE ..JUST CLICK )
Situated in exclusive Botanic Ridge, is this huge 4BR family home only 7 years young. Located only short walk or golf cart ride to country club including gym, pool,restaurant and golf course.1 min walk to huge sparks park.
Botanic ridge offers 6km approx of walking and running trails and only mins to connecting freeways, high percentage of families living in the estate and 80% owner occpancy.
Offering HUGE benefits as follows
• 40 squares under roof line
• Gigantic 1152 sqm block approx. with side access and huge backyard
• Home theatre room or another living area
• Huge Master suite with boutique style bathroom and massive walk in robe
• Twin basin and spa bath in ensuite
• State of art kitchen with white gloss cabinetry and stone benchtop with stainless steel appliances
• Separate enclosed study or home office area with bench and seperate powder room
• Covered alfresco area for entertaining all year round with added bonus of side deck and paved areas
• Side access for boat or caravan storage leading to workshop/shed
• 3 living areas for the largest of families
• Recently added outdoor blinds, indoor screens on doors, cameras, new paving and concrete areas, security doors, and solar panels (6.6 kw) saving you loads in power bills
This one is sure to impress and ticks all the boxes! Inspect now
